59/* gimple_build, functionally matching fold_buildN, outputs stmts
60 int the provided sequence, matching and simplifying them on-the-fly.
61 Supposed to replace force_gimple_operand (fold_buildN (...), ...). */
62extern tree gimple_build (gimple_seq *, location_t,
63 enum tree_code, tree, tree);
64inline tree
65gimple_build (gimple_seq *seq,
66 enum tree_code code, tree type, tree op0)
67{
68 return gimple_build (seq, UNKNOWN_LOCATION, code, type, op0);
69}
